query:
SELECT 
  i.id,
  i.productId,
  p.sku,
  p.description,
  i.tenantId,
  t.name as tenantName,
  i.quantity,
  wl.code as locationCode
FROM inventory i
LEFT JOIN products p ON i.productId = p.id
LEFT JOIN tenants t ON i.tenantId = t.id
LEFT JOIN warehouseLocations wl ON i.locationId = wl.id
WHERE i.productId IN (180001, 180003, 180004)
ORDER BY i.productId, i.id
LIMIT 20;
